README.md

Awesome

     A curated list of
     [file://localhost/Users/admin/Pros/sh/awesome/awe_raw/awesome-steam#
     packages]packages and
     [file://localhost/Users/admin/Pros/sh/awesome/awe_raw/awesome-steam#
     resources]resources regarding [http://store.steampowered.com/]Steam
     development.

   Please read the
   co
   ntribution guidelines before contributing.

   The purpose of this document is to provide a quick overview over
   existing packages (libraries, modules etc.) and resources available
   regarding Steam client automation and WebAPI usage. Whenever you need
   to start a new project, have a look at the list of packages and see if
   there is anything useful for your use case. If you need technical
   details or tutorials, check out the resources section.

Table of Contents

     * Packages
          + Node.js
          + C#
          + PHP
          + Go
          + Python
          + C++
          + Java
          + Objective-C
     * Resources
          + General
          + Tutorials
          + Posts
          + Standalone Tools
          + Discussion Boards
          + Third-Party Services

Packages

     ¡ Many of these package repositories provide helpful READMEs and
     wiki pages, which explain the usage and/or provide examples. Do not
     forget to check them out when using particular package.

Node.js

General

     * [https://github.com/seishun/node-steam]steam - Interface directly
       with Steam servers from Node.js.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-client]steam-client -
       API-compatible fork of node-steam's SteamClient.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-user]steam-user -
       Feature-rich easy-to-use Steam client.
     * [https://github.com/scholtzm/vapor]vapor - Lightweight Steam client
       framework.
     * [https://github.com/dragonbanshee/node-steam-parentbot]steam-parent
       bot - Simple base class for a Steam bot.

WebAPI

     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-webapi]steam-webapi -
       Complete WebAPI wrapper with support for extra HTTP headers sent by
       Steam.
     * [https://github.com/lloti/node-steamapi]steamapi - A nice Steam API
       wrapper.

Trading

     * [https://github.com/seishun/node-steam-trade]steam-trade - Node.js
       wrapper around Steam live trading.
     * [https://github.com/Alex7Kom/node-steam-tradeoffers]steam-tradeoffe
       rs - Steam Trade Offers for Node.js.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-tradeoffer-manager]steam
       -tradeoffer-manager - Simple and sane Steam trade offer management.

Game Interaction

     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-gameserver]steam-gameser
       ver - Steam client handler for Gameserver and AnonGameserver
       account types.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-tf2]tf2 - Interact directly
       with TF2 game coordinator.
     * [https://github.com/joshuaferrara/node-csgo]csgo - Interact
       directly with CS:GO game coordinator.
     * [https://github.com/RJacksonm1/node-dota2]dota2 - Interact directly
       with Dota 2 game coordinator.

Community & Store Automation

     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steamcommunity]steamcommunity
       - Interact with steamcommunity.com. Also allows to confirm trade
       offers.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steamstore]steamstore -
       Interact with store.steampowered.com.
     * [https://github.com/Alex7Kom/node-steam-weblogon]steam-weblogon -
       Retrieve SteamCommunity cookies if you are running Steam network
       client.
     * [https://github.com/Alex7Kom/node-steam-web-api-key]steam-web-api-k
       ey - Automatically registers and retrieves Steam API key.
     * [https://github.com/Alex7Kom/node-steam-parental]steam-parental -
       Disable parental lock.

Authentication

     * [https://github.com/cpancake/steam-login]steam-login - Simple
       Connect / Express Steam authentication library.
     * [https://github.com/liamcurry/passport-steam]passport-steam - Steam
       (OpenID) authentication strategy for Passport and Node.js.
     * [https://github.com/scholtzm/meteor-accounts-steam]meteor-accounts-
       steam - Steam OpenID integration for Meteor Accounts.

Misc

     * [https://github.com/seishun/node-steam-resources]steam-resources -
       Steam's enums, protobufs and structs.
     * [https://github.com/seishun/node-steam-crypto]steam-crypto -
       Node.js implementation of Steam crypto.
     * [https://github.com/scholtzm/node-steam-groups]steam-groups -
       Custom node-steam handler which provides group functions.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steamid]steamid - SteamID
       usage and conversion made easy.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-totp]steam-totp - Easily
       generate 2FA codes used by Steam.
     * [https://github.com/Steam-Chat-Bot/node-steam-chat-bot]steam-chat-b
       ot - Simplified interface for a steam chat bot.
     * [https://github.com/RJacksonm1/node-vdf]vdf - vdf to object and
       vice versa.
     * [https://github.com/scholtzm/node-steamrep]steamrep - Check user's
       SteamRep reputation.
     * [https://github.com/scholtzm/node-reptf]reptf - Check user's rep.tf
       reputation.

C#

General

     * [https://github.com/SteamRE/SteamKit]SteamKit2 - .NET library
       designed to interoperate with Valve's Steam network.
     * [https://github.com/geel9/SteamAuth]SteamAuth - A C# library that
       provides vital Steam Mobile Authenticator functionality.
     * [https://github.com/Jessecar96/SteamBot]SteamBot - Automated bot
       software for interacting with steam trade.
     * [https://github.com/waylaidwanderer/SteamTradeOffersBot]SteamTradeO
       ffersBot - SteamBot fork which focuses on trade offers.
     * [https://github.com/ObsidianMinor/SteamStandardProject]SteamStandar
       dProject - A collection of .NET Standard libraries using common
       types that provide functionality in one or more parts of Steam.

Misc

     * [https://github.com/igeligel/BackpackLogin]BackpackLogin - A .NET
       Standard library for logging into backpack.tf using Steam
       credentials.
     * [https://github.com/igeligel/TeamFortressOutpostApi]TeamFortressOut
       postApi - A .NET Standard class library which allows user to
       interact with TF2Outpost.
     * [https://github.com/igeligel/SteamGaugesApi]SteamGaugesApi - A .NET
       Standard 2.0 library to automatically use the API of
       [https://steamgaug.es/]steamgauges.

PHP

     * [https://github.com/waylaidwanderer/PHP-SteamCommunity]SteamCommuni
       ty - A PHP library for interacting with the Steam Community
       website.
     * [https://github.com/SmItH197/SteamAuthentication]SteamAuthenticatio
       n - Steam OpenID authentication with PHP.
     * [https://github.com/BlackCetha/SteamAuthOOP]SteamAuthOOP - An
       object-oriented alternative to SteamAuthentication.
     * [https://github.com/DaMitchell/steam-api-php]steam-api - A PHP
       wrapper for the Steam API.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/php-steamid]steamid - SteamID class
       for PHP.
     * [https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/php-steam-totp]steam-totp - PHP
       library to deal with Steam's proprietary TOTP algorithm.
     * [https://github.com/vikas5914/steam-auth]steam-auth - An
       alternative Steam authentication library with Composer support.

Go

     * [https://github.com/Philipp15b/go-steam]steam - Steam's protocol in
       Go.
     * [https://github.com/YellowOrWhite/go-steam-mobileauth]steam-mobilea
       uth - Port of SteamAuth in Go.

Python

General

     * [https://github.com/ValvePython/steam]steam - Module for various
       interactions with Steam.
     * [https://bitbucket.org/AzuiSleet/pysteamkit]PySteamKit - Python
       port of SteamKit.
     * [https://github.com/Lagg/steamodd]steamodd - Steam tools library.
     * [https://github.com/bukson/steampy]steampy - Fully automated Steam
       trade offers library with SteamGuard support.
     * [https://github.com/smiley/steamapi]SteamAPI - An object-oriented
       Python 2.7+ library for accessing the Steam Web API.
     * [https://github.com/Zwork101/steam-trade]Steam-Trade - An
       asynchronous, event-based trade library.

Game Interaction

     * [https://github.com/ValvePython/csgo]csgo - Python module for
       interacting with CSGO's Game Coordinator.
     * [https://github.com/ValvePython/dota2]dota2 - Python module for
       interacting with Dota 2's Game Coordinator.

Misc

     * [https://github.com/ValvePython/vpk]vpk - Python module for working
       with Valve's Pack format.
     * [https://github.com/ValvePython/vdf]vdf - Python module for working
       with Valve's KeyValue format.

C++

     * [https://github.com/seishun/SteamPP]SteamPP - C++ library to
       interoperate with Steam servers.

Java

     * [https://github.com/Top-Cat/SteamKit-Java]SteamKit-Java - Java port
       of SteamKit.

Objective-C

     * [https://github.com/michaelchum/SteamAuth]SteamAuth - An iOS
       wrapper around Steam's OpenID login.

Resources

General

     * [https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/Steam_Web_API]Steam
       WebAPI @ ValveSoftware
     * [https://wiki.teamfortress.com/wiki/WebAPI]Steam WebAPI @ TF2 Wiki
     * [https://lab.xpaw.me/steam_api_documentation.html]Steam WebAPI
       Documentation by xpaw
     * [http://steamcommunity.com/dev]Steam as OpenID Provider
     * [http://steamcommunity.com/dev/apikey]Steam API Key Registration
     * [https://steamerrors.com/]Steam Error Codes - List of EResult codes
       with possible explanations.

Tutorials

     * [https://firepowered.org/developer/create-a-steam-trade-bot-with-no
       dejs-iojs-updated-for-node-steam-v1-0/]Creating a Steam Trade Bot
       with Node.js
     * [https://github.com/charredgrass/nodejs-bot-guide]Charred's node.js
       Guide to Steam Bots
     * [https://github.com/andrewda/node-steam-guide]In-depth Steam Bot
       Guide with Node.js
     * [http://forums.backpack.tf/index.php?/topic/45995-guide-how-to-get-
       your-shared-secret-from-ios-device-steam-mobile/]Retrieving 2FA
       Keys from iOS Device

Posts

     * [https://dev.doctormckay.com/topic/332-identifying-steam-items/]Ite
       m IDs Explained
     * [https://www.reddit.com/r/SteamBot/comments/3udhkd/everything_relat
       ed_to_escrow/]Everything Related to Escrow
     * [https://www.reddit.com/r/SteamBot/comments/3cv6k7/problem_download
       ing_an_avatar_using/]Understanding Avatar Hash

Standalone Tools

     * [https://github.com/SteamRE/SteamKit/tree/master/Resources/NetHook2
       ]NetHook2 - Intercept Steam client's network messages.
     * [https://github.com/SteamRE/SteamKit/tree/master/Resources/NetHookA
       nalyzer2]NetHook2 Analyzer - Inspect messages dumped by NetHook2.
     * [http://scholtzm.github.io/steam-auth-web-util/]steam-auth-web-util
       - Generate 2FA codes directly in your web browser.
     * [https://github.com/Jessecar96/SteamDesktopAuthenticator]SteamDeskt
       opAuthenticator - Desktop implementation of Steam's mobile
       authenticator app.

Discussion Boards

     * [https://www.reddit.com/r/SteamBot]/r/SteamBot
     * [https://discord.gg/0i5X3oDHJbDUsiGC]/r/SteamBot Discord
     * [https://www.reddit.com/r/nodesteam]/r/nodesteam
     * [https://dev.doctormckay.com/]DoctorMcKay's Dev Forum
     * [https://github.com/steam-forward/node-steam-forum]node-steam-forum

Third-Party Services

   Websites listed below may provide free and/or paid services and are
   listed alphabetically according to their domain name.
     * [https://backpack.tf/developer]backpack.tf - Provides TF2 prices
       and Steam market/inventory related services.
     * [https://steamanalyst.com/]steamanalyst.com - Provides CS:GO
       prices.
     * [https://steamapi.io/]steamapi.io - Provides prices for several
       games and Steam market/inventory related services.
     * [https://steamapis.com/]steamapis.com - Provides prices for several
       games and Steam market/inventory related services.
     * [https://steamlytics.xyz/]steamlytics.xyz - Provides CS:GO prices
       and Steam market/inventory related services.

